name: Multirostro 2,a videoimage.
description: A video-composition in the guise of a flower, a rose, inspired by Umberto Eco's novel. The name of the rose is forever unknown. A portrait, juxtaposed thrice to remain disguised in the image. What is in an image after all? Made from a digital copy study of  detail of "Dream of Spring"(1901), by French painter William Bouguereau (1825-1905). year of creation:2021.
